6	
7	/**
8	 * Account Router
9	 *
10	 * Manages user account profile information from Clerk.
11	 * This router contains only non-table-based operations.
12	 *
13	 * Table-based operations have been moved to:
14	 * - API Keys: org-api-keys router (org-scoped)
15	 * - Integrations: user-sources router
16	 */
